Split Transformation: Break Up Column Values

In a Transform node of a Data Prep recipe, select the text (dimension) column in the Preview tab.
Select the delimiter in the Delimiter field.
Specify the column labels for both new columns.
Click Apply to add the transformation to the Transform node.

Going back to the address example, the Address field is split into two.
If needed, add the Split transformation again to further split the column values.

To view the Graph area, click the Collapse button.
Save the recipe.
